entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="kor" o="어이! 여기! 여기야!" t="Hey! Pssst! Hey, you!" b="" a=""/>
Are you Hwangbo?
You Hwangbo?
<kiroshi l="kor" o="그래. 근데 다들 날 \"치타\"라고 불러. 내가 또 치타처럼 존나 빠르거든." t="Yeah. But everyone calls me \"Cheetah.\" 'Cuz y'know, I'm fast like a cheetah." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="kor" o="이런 개씨발! 놈들이야!" t="Shit, shit, shit, they're here!" b="" a=""/>
Do I look blind or deaf to you?
<kiroshi l="kor" o="으... 씨발 존나 아슬아슬했는데 그래도 우리가 해냈어." t="Uff... That was a close call, but we did it." b="" a=""/>
Not my concern.
Regina knows what she's doing.
Not my concern.
<kiroshi l="kor" o="야, 야. 그럼 이건 어때? 날 다시 도시로 데려다주면..." t="'Ey, wait, how about this – you take me back to the city and..." b="" a=""/>
Out, or I'll harvest those kidneys myself.
Reggie hired 'em direct. Ran the spec herself.
Regina sends her regards.
<kiroshi l="kor" o="알았어, 알았다고. 내리면 되잖아. 그리고... 모텔에서 도와줘서 고마웠어." t="OK. OK. I'm going. And... thanks for your help back at the motel." b="" a=""/>
Any time.
Let me do the driving.
<kiroshi l="kor" o="그럼 난? 난 뭐 하면 되는데?" t="And me? What am I supposed to do?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="kor" o="어이, 넌 별명 같은 거 없어?" t="'Ey, you got some kinda nickname?" b="" a=""/>
Nope.
<kiroshi l="kor" o="저런, 그럼 이참에 뭐라도 생각해 놔. 길거리에서 존나 잘 먹힐 테니까." t="Damn, well you gotta come up with something. Street cred'll thank you for it." b="" a=""/>
Is that so?
<kiroshi l="kor" o="당연하지. 그냥 입에 착 붙는 거로 아무거나 지어내 봐. 그럼 사람들이 금방 기억할 거야." t="Totally. Just start calling yourself something and people'll catch onto it in no time." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="kor" o="난 효과 좀 봤거든." t="Worked for me, it did." b="" a=""/>
Nobody calls you that.
OK, "Cheetah."
Nobody calls you that.
OK, "Cheetah," whatever. I don't care. Long as you're good for it.
How'd you get here?
Shut your trap if you don't wanna eat lead.
"We?"
You deserve a medal.
"We?" If it wasn't for me, you'd be a stain on a motel floor.
You want a medal or something?
Just don't dirty up my ride, OK?
Don't dirty up my ride.
Just stay quiet.
Just stay put an' quiet.
OK, we're here. Get out.
<kiroshi l="kor" o="잠깐, 근데... 저 새끼들 믿어도 돼? 너 가면 내 콩팥 떼 가고 그러는 건 아니지?" t="Wait, but... Are those guys cool? They won't harvest my kidneys the second you leave?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="kor" o="차 타고 왔지. 걸어왔겠냐? 이 근처에 주차해 뒀어." t="By car. Parked not too far from here." b="" a=""/>
You drive, then. I'll make sure you stay alive.
